#. <section class="sutta" id="sn4.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. Life Span"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 8. Nandatisutta → nandanasuttaṃ (s1-3) | nandanaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "sn4.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Nandatisutta"
msgstr "8. Delighting"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "sn4.8:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "sn4.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn4.8:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato "
"santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and recited this verse in the "
"Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.108"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.241"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.1"
msgid "“Nandati puttehi puttimā,"
msgstr "“Your children bring you delight!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.2"
msgid "Gomā gobhi tatheva nandati;"
msgstr "Your cattle also bring you delight!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.3"
msgid "Upadhīhi narassa nandanā,"
msgstr "For attachments are a man’s delight;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:2.4"
msgid "Na hi so nandati yo nirūpadhī”ti."
msgstr "without attachments there’s no delight.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.1"
msgid "“Socati puttehi puttimā,"
msgstr "“Your children bring you sorrow."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.2"
msgid "Gomā gobhi tatheva socati;"
msgstr "Your cattle also bring you sorrow."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.3"
msgid "Upadhīhi narassa socanā,"
msgstr "For attachments are a man’s sorrow;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.8:3.4"
msgid "Na hi so socati yo nirūpadhī”ti."
msgstr "without attachments there are no sorrows.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.8:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā “jānāti maṃ bhagavā, jānāti maṃ sugato”ti dukkhī "
"dummano tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then Māra the Wicked, thinking, “The Buddha knows me! The Holy One knows me!”"
" miserable and sad, vanished right there."
